msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: apache2.xml:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>apxs2</command> enables the compilation and installation of modules from source code (including the required changes to the configuration files), which creates <emphasis>dynamic shared objects</emphasis> (DSOs) that can be loaded into Apache at runtime."
