msgid "To enable Apache to deliver content created by CGI scripts, <systemitem>mod_cgi</systemitem> needs to be activated. <systemitem>mod_alias</systemitem> is also needed. Both modules are enabled by default. Refer to <xref linkend=\"sec-apache2-modules-activating\"/> for details on activating modules."
