msgid "<emphasis>If you have configured your custom CGI directory, is it configured properly?</emphasis> If in doubt, try the script within the default CGI directory <filename>/srv/www/cgi-bin/</filename> and call it with <literal>http://localhost/cgi-bin/test.cgi</literal> ."
